OL,3,CMan jailed for 15 years over plot to
OL,4,Cattack Taylor Swift concert in Vienna
OL,6,FA man who admitted planning to attack
OL,7,Fa Taylor Swift concert in Vienna
OL,8,Fnearly two years ago has been
OL,9,Fsentenced to 15 years in prison.
OL,11,FThe 21-year-old defendant, known only
OL,12,Fas Beran A. under Austrian privacy
OL,13,Frules, had planned to target people
OL,14,Foutside the Ernst Happel Stadium with
OL,15,Fknives or homemade explosives in
OL,16,FAugust 2024, the court was told.
OL,18,FThe plot was thwarted following a tip
OL,19,Foff from the CIA, but Swift's three
OL,20,Fconcerts were still cancelled, leaving
OL,21,Faround 200,000 fans devastated.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
