OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780045514
OL,3,CMan jailed for 15 years over plot to
OL,4,Cattack Taylor Swift concert in Vienna
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FIn his final words to the court before
OL,12,Fit adjourned to consider a verdict on
OL,13,FThursday, Beran A. said: "I would just
OL,14,Flike to say that I am sorry."
OL,16,FBeran A. was also found guilty of
OL,17,Faiding and abetting attempted murder
OL,18,Fand for encouraging his former school
OL,19,Ffriend Hasan E. in a knife attack in
OL,20,FMecca, Saudi Arabia, the court heard.
