PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780045514
OL,3,CMan jailed for 15 years over plot to
OL,4,Cattack Taylor Swift concert in Vienna
OL,6,FThe two men and co-defendant Arda K.
OL,7,Fwere accused of planning three attacks
OL,8,Fbetween them as part of a terrorist
OL,9,Fcell.
OL,11,FBeran A. had pleaded guilty to the
OL,12,Fcharges relating to the concert plot
OL,13,Fon the first day of his trial in April.
OL,15,FHe had hoped to "kill as many people
OL,16,Fas possible" in the planned attack,
OL,17,Fauthorities said in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
