PN,31104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780045514
OL,3,CMan jailed for 15 years over plot to
OL,4,Cattack Taylor Swift concert in Vienna
OL,6,FThe court heard he had networked with
OL,7,Fother members of the Islamic State
OL,8,Fgroup, ahead of the attack to discuss
OL,9,Fthe purchase of weapons and had sworn
OL,10,Fallegiance to the militant group.
OL,12,FAuthorities searched his apartment the
OL,13,Fday he was arrested and allegedly
OL,14,Ffound bomb-making materials.
OL,16,FSwift learned about the bomb plot
OL,17,Fwhile on the plane to Austria and
OL,18,Flater said the tour had narrowly
OL,19,F"dodged a massacre situation" in her
OL,20,Fdocumentary of the Eras Tour.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
