PN,31105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780045514
OL,3,CMan jailed for 15 years over plot to
OL,4,Cattack Taylor Swift concert in Vienna
OL,6,F"Having our Vienna shows cancelled was
OL,7,Fdevastating," Swift wrote in a
OL,8,Fstatement posted to Instagram two
OL,9,Fweeks after she cancelled the shows.
OL,11,F"The reason for the cancellations
OL,12,Ffilled me with a new sense of fear,
OL,13,Fand a tremendous amount of guilt
OL,14,Fbecause so many people had planned on
OL,15,Fcoming to those shows."
OL,17,FBeran A. was tried alongside Arda K.,
OL,18,Fanother 21-year-old whose full name
OL,19,Falso has not been made public, but
OL,20,Fonly he was charged in connection with
OL,21,Fthe concert plot.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
