FL,312,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F311A1780045514
OL,3,CMan jailed for 15 years over plot to
OL,4,Cattack Taylor Swift concert in Vienna
OL,6,FBoth defendants, along with Hasan E.,
OL,7,Fwere accused of planning to carry out
OL,8,Fsimultaneous attacks in Saudi Arabia,
OL,9,FTurkey and the United Arab Emirates
OL,10,Fduring Ramadan 2024 in the name of
OL,11,FIslamic State.
OL,13,FBeran A. pleaded not guilty to the
OL,14,Fcharges related to the plot for
OL,15,Fsimultaneous attacks, but both he and
OL,16,FArda K. were convicted of allegedly
OL,17,Fcontributing to attempted murder in
OL,18,FSaudi Arabia, Austria Press Agency
OL,19,Freported.
OL,21,FArda K. was given a 12-year sentence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
